{"tid":541343,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(突發)袁澧林同男友係日本瘋狂造愛11日😭😭","createTime":"2018-01-26T10:16:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-30T13:40:32.000Z","uid":49648,"like":23,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"3c1e3802e22941e026b3ecc57d06c5f3fc4ba141","tid":541343,"uid":49648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T10:16:03.000Z","msg":"佢男友就好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 知唔知係咪有錢仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wAPAKPge_nI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FwAPAKPge_nI&d=Im9tYpnO5s2wl9WWYDs3S5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=f14f1089\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wAPAKPge_nI</a><br />\n「文青女神」袁澧林（Angela）出席活動。談及情人節，她表示會與男友以及一班朋友到日本旅行：「都好耐冇放過假，之前都有機會放，但自己係工作狂又驚夾唔到期，終於新年拍電影收爐就唔使開工。」她表示旅程長達11日，會去東京及北海道滑雪。問到叻唔叻滑雪？她說：「之前同個好癲嘅大學同學都唔係好理安全，去過四川喺冇裝備同教練教嘅情況下滑過，打咗幾個翻，希望今次喺日本可以正常咁滑雪。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63066e2dbe273a6d7c052753dc0fed36f4cc7b58","tid":541343,"uid":44454,"like":80,"dislike":8,"score":72,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T10:23:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/26/182300_529436460d4c73c15de470f8f0265249.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F26%2F182300_529436460d4c73c15de470f8f0265249.png&h=8289a1e3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4ce64c5e50d0f749867059c66151a4c52a8e4a55","tid":541343,"uid":61018,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T10:56:12.000Z","msg":"男友同一班朋友<br />\n多p"},{"pid":"8b087c62aafe84de5dec88d72c242c90320dc40f","tid":541343,"uid":3549,"like":41,"dislike":3,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T11